Epule Jeffrey Ewusi (a mụrụ na 6 Nọvemba 1983) bụ onye Cameroon na-eme ihe nkiri nke a maara maka ihe nkiri dịka Breach of Trust, Red Pink Poison (2013), Decoded(2013) na Royal destination nke gosipụtara Tonto Dikeh na Emeka Ike. O meela ihe nkiri ihe karịrị iri atọ na ise. N'afọ 2012, a họpụtara ya ma merie Cameroon Entertainment Award dịka nwoke kachasị mma na-eme ihe nkiri na 2012 DAMA kacha mma maka ihe nkiri Decoded
A mụrụ Epule Jeffrey Ewusi na Buea South west Region nke Cameroon
Ọ bụ onye Bakosian site n'ebo, ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị PNEU na Bamenda, Bilingual Grammar School (Lycee) Molyko na Buea wee nweta iwu na Public Law n'afọ 2006 na Mahadum Yaounde II.
Jeffrey, anọwo na-eme ihe nkiri kemgbe afọ 2012 ruo ugbu a
Na-egosi na ihe karịrị ihe nkiri 35 na Cinema nke Cameroon na Nollywood na Naịjirịa. Ọ pụtara na usoro telivishọn a na-akpọ Zamba, nke a na-egosi na Cameroon Radio Television (CRTV).
